 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"主席：鄭松泰議員要求點名表決。表決鐘會響 5 分鐘。<br />\n <br />\n鄭松泰議員反對。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主席宣布經由功能團體選舉產生的議員，有 22 人出席，20 人贊成，1 人棄權；而經由分區直接選舉產生的議員，有 15 人出席，14 人贊成，1 人反對。由於議題獲得兩部分在席議員分別以過半數贊成，他於是宣布議案獲得通過。"},{"pid":"1e2b32e5c6bcfe6fad65083e8526e5478b3ae655","tid":2395139,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1185f45580672dd6f62e6a65811b552499b2251d","tid":2395139,"uid":311626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"開相機扮影咪得，大亨教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"謝偉銓議員：但過去數年的經驗告訴我，在立法會，真的甚麼事情也可能發生，包括搶手機、搶文件、擲&quot;臭彈&quot;、毆打保安人員、宣誓變為&quot;宣獨&quot;等，我相信事前很少人會想到，但事實上是有人這樣做。<span class=\"red\">以黑客入侵等方式擾亂、&quot;惡搞&quot;立法會的視像會議，把正在參與會議的議員改頭換面，配上另一把聲音，製造畫面的時差，令&quot;贊成&quot;變成&quot;反對&quot;，將來又會否發生呢？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有關做法是否違反《立法會(權力及特權)條例》呢？是否等同妨礙議員開會及干擾立法會實體會議的進行呢？這些都可能是我們要關注的問題。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210114/photo/bkn-20210114132929786-0114_00822_001_01b.jpg?20210114222821\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210114%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210114132929786-0114_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20210114222821&h=0e4d6595&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5954fcbc02789cad31c48f795fb5c470c4477ccf","tid":2395139,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea8ddb7c52767cf78885c0afdb1b08d11feedf55","tid":2395139,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地泰博堅守議會陣線<br />\n唯一反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"<em>政府在政治上無所作為，作為建制中人，他們此刻就應思想出一些點子，用以欺騙自己的支持者也是需要的，但他們卻沒有，只顧說防疫、防疫、防疫，當涉及他們的範圍時，他們便&quot;咿嘩鬼叫&quot;，例如在維多利亞公園賣桔一事。<span class=\"gold\">我不談政治，因為這並非我能處理的範疇。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},{"pid":"c36869bfa585dcd0761d03648ed9f268d328a6d1","tid":2395139,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b92ebf0213a27fe7d6c9b418ca4cb79c096157e7","tid":2395139,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"張相大亨勁能型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a419a554941586ef06e945297fad75d702ffd1","tid":2395139,"uid":166262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"死熱狗 blocked"},{"pid":"344c99a1b5f3dbabbc637e69bf48305a15e93218","tid":2395139,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a419a554941586ef06e945297fad75d702ffd1","tid":2395139,"uid":166262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"死熱狗 blocked"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa